{"tid":667380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：中國是時候付出更多","createTime":"2018-05-16T16:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T02:57:21.000Z","uid":147314,"like":43,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"524bb1e20e3a05fe00813d3a4c529c8a5127b29f","tid":667380,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T16:45:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1845094/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1845094%2F&d=1%2B%2BDnvUxsbC2G6xB3tx739tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4ca815e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1845094/</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普:中國是時候應付出更多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/05/16/1845094_6e44e5c06b42ea2d309be0190a204763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F1845094_6e44e5c06b42ea2d309be0190a204763.jpg&h=7fe44f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國務院副總理劉鶴今日已抵達華盛頓，與美國高層團隊繼續磋商解決中美貿易磨擦。<br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒早前引述知情人士指，中美正商討若美國放寬對中興通訊(00763)的禁令，中方將撤回向美國農產品加徵關稅的反制措施。<br />\n<br />\n不過，美國總統特朗普在Twitter帖文指出，美國媒體相關報道是假新聞，並批評過往美國官員在中美貿易談判中表現欠佳，導致美國每年對華貿易上損失數千億美元，美國過去付出太多，現時只能作出少許讓步，反而中國應付出更多。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又稱，目前美方仍未收到中方要求，並稱中興通訊事件與兩國達成更大的貿易協議無關。"},{"pid":"2643cc5222cca02b862e9cbd87a7bbc9dc35a435","tid":667380,"uid":31098,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T16:50:02.000Z","msg":"媽，我好亂啊.jpg"},{"pid":"ca781989882d7a26510724b51f3badb8d96f09d1","tid":667380,"uid":41245,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T16:51:08.000Z","msg":"所以話華霉啲字眼有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個意思係要中國付出返同等嘅嘢<br />\n但華霉係要用「付出更多」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到好似無理要求噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51434379b544b57f10351d159a33a75612a368f2","tid":667380,"uid":68285,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"ca781989882d7a26510724b51f3badb8d96f09d1","tid":667380,"uid":41245,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T16:51:08.000Z","msg":"所以話華霉啲字眼有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個意思係要中國付出返同等嘅嘢<br />\n但華霉係要用「付出更多」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到好似無理要求噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T16:55:48.000Z","msg":"梗係啦<br />\n<br />\n班五毛以為貿易戰係美國做緊攻方 支那係守方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實情贏國係進攻一方  呢十幾年黎食左咁多錢  仲透過2025想做埋第一<br />\n<br />\n依家美國先被逼還手   要吸精瓶噁番出黎"},{"pid":"9ed29f1af7135cf52d7102c07ba0be644aacad28","tid":667380,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f65193038ef1be4d09619a83e9f37d2e573233e0","tid":667380,"uid":56321,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T17:24:56.000Z","msg":"[突發] 有人在白宮聯署網站提出凍結香港政策法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/658941/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/658941/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署link：<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-president-trump-freeze-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpetition-president-trump-freeze-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act&d=1%2B%2BDnvUxsbC2G6xB3tx739tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=cdf1dce9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/petition-president-trump-freeze-united-states-hong-kong-policy-act</a><br />\n<br />\n因為Trump彈弓手想放生中興，襯而家中興件事係美國鬧大咗同爭議大咗<br />\n<br />\n